1	N2 + O -> NO + N
2	O2 + N -> NO + O
3	NO + N -> N2 + O (REV)
4	NO + O -> O2 + N (REV)


#********************************
#list of reactions (without multiple limits)
1	N2 + O -> NO + N
2	NO + N -> N2 + O (REV)
3	O2 + N -> NO + O
4	NO + O -> O2 + N (REV)


